To run:

Windows:
pip install pyaudio

Mac/Linux:
sudo apt install -y portaudio19-dev
sudo apt install -y pyaudio
pip install pyaudio

if pip install does not work:
check python version with python --version
install corresponding file for correct version from: https://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/#pyaudio
put downloaded .whl file in pyvoice folder
run pip install PyAudio-0.2.11-xxx-xxx-xxx-xxx, corresponding to file name